        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27632047/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/27632047/" class="">第1页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/BZleon/" class=" " title="安然比丘">安然比丘</a>
              
                <span class="allstar30" title="还行"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="27632047">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">以己之昏昏，焉能使人昭昭</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2013-07-17 13:34</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                以己之昏昏，焉能使人昭昭
